{title: Jesus Is A Good Ole Boy}
{artist: Cal Smith}
{composer: Written by Hank Cochran and Hollis Rudolph DeLaughter}

[C]To old folks Jesus is a [F]place to [C]go
To children Jesus is a [D7]brand new [G7]toy
[C]But I know something that [F]they don't [C]know
Cause to me Jesus is a [G7]good ole [C]boy
Most folks think Jesus ain't a [F]mortal [C]man
Just something they're hoping and [D7]praying [G7]for
